{"tid":2371493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"餅店結業心血付諸流水 60歲「過來人」毛舜筠為餐廳倒閉潮心痛:特別替食肆難過","createTime":"2021-01-19T02:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T03:27:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fa14940bf5984c8302d2a076d484da443d1c66","tid":2371493,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"壹週刊 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_773603_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773603_0&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4b40a9c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773603_0&h=adb03a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_773603_0</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情肆虐，至今第四波依然反覆，防疫足足一年的港人，難免出現抗疫疲勞。<br />\n<br />\n疫情去到第四波，許多餐廳開始撐不住陸續結業，而一向對美食有研究，曾遠赴日本及法國修讀藍帶課程的藝人毛舜筠，於18年開自己親手造的曲奇餅店，可惜開業一年就撐不住結業，她形容是人生中最失意的一年，故對香港食肆面臨倒閉，明白箇中心血付諸流水的痛，她跟本刊談到疫情睇法時，以過來人心情不禁為餐飲界感嘆:「特別替食肆感到難過，非常痛心。」"},{"pid":"3374691734898c2f450597d11949ef8207bb6ce8","tid":2371493,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"香港唔興食曲奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a988227fca1eb110f43801585b64ef84bdeb420","tid":2371493,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3374691734898c2f450597d11949ef8207bb6ce8","tid":2371493,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"香港唔興食曲奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"俾鋪租頂死<br />\n做網上銷售先做到"},{"pid":"281a3eb4063714156b426a49f2f47f85818dd15c","tid":2371493,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3374691734898c2f450597d11949ef8207bb6ce8","tid":2371493,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"香港唔興食曲奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"香港人甜嘢要食軟 鹹嘢要食硬<br />\n嗰啲手作曲奇唔軟唔硬唔係香港人口味"}]}